  pearl_lily:{name:L("The Wreath of Pearl Lilies"), lore:L("White lilies for her hair, each leaf half a pearl, and eight great oysters clasped to her tail. 'Pride must suffer pain,' the old queen said — and it did.")},
  magic_draught:{name:L("The Witch's Draught"), lore:L("Clear as the purest water, sharp as a two-edged sword. It bought her legs and a chance at a soul — and cost her tongue, her home, and every certainty but love.")},
