  {key:"bala", name:ALTYN_NAME.bala, role:alt("The Rich Man's Only Son"), path:"bala",
   power:alt("You are the longed-for son, given a knucklebone of gold — and, unknown to you, promised to a witch of the lake. Ride the mangy colt that becomes a tulpar, outwit the Jalmauyz Kempir, and find your way home.")}
